          "Character2dId": 272
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki's Sister's Message",
      "Body": "'I think making the pattern from scratch will be a bit difficult, so I'll send you some pattern data I made a long time ago. Try altering things using this as a base.'",
